<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Don't bother even looking at the price quotes. If they think you can buy this belt for 9k plat, they are dreaming. The reed belt sells for around 8k, and often trades for a Ykesha, or SMR, when non WIS users get one. In the planes, non-clerics aren't even allowed to roll for this item, unless every cleric in zone has one, and they won't. This is a very rare drop. This belt gives a high AC modifier at that level, and adds around 15 hps due to the +5 Stamina. The only belt like this I have seen even sell, traded for a Haste sash, 2 Ykeshas, a mithril 2h sword, and a FULL set of crafted armor. The cleric buying it though he was lucky. To add insult to injury, my level 1 cleric's wearing one.</font></td></tr></table>
